## Financial Targets & Revenue Model

To support the ongoing research, the project has set an annual revenue target of **$300,000 USD**. The diversified revenue model is structured as follows:

| Revenue Stream | Annual Target | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Ko-fi Donations** | $30,000 USD | Monthly recurring support from the community. |
| **Digital Content** | $120,000 USD | Sales of PDF guides and interactive Jupyter notebooks. |
| **Workshops** | $150,000 USD | Seasonal online technical workshops. |

